author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Has the streaming bubble burst for Disney? With hundreds of layoffs and billions in debt, the gamble of Disney+ doesn't seem to have paid off. And with rumours of emergency reshoots and poor test screenings, is Fanastic Four destined to be an M-She-U disaster? Join me, MauLer, Random Film Talk, Echo Chamberlain and Box Office Brawler as we find out. 

Subscribe to Random Film Talk: https://www.youtube.com/@randomft
Subscribe to Echo: https://www.youtube.com/@EchoChamberlain
Subscribe to Brawler: https://www.youtube.com/@BoxOfficeBrawler
title: Open Bar #145 - Disney Layoffs, Fantastic Four Girlbosses, Streaming Killing Hollywood?
